CanvasApp.Description: Reservation parking lets users reserve slot for a specific parking slot/option in advance. This will allow for the pre-allocation of parking and have a better inventory of parking slots. Allowing parkers to secure their spot ahead of time through a digital experience will both be beneficial to the parkers and the parking management.
